{%- comment -%}
  Shelzy's Designs - Font Preloading Snippet

  HOW TO USE:
  1. Go to Online Store > Themes > Actions > Edit code
  2. In the Snippets folder, click "Add a new snippet"
  3. Name it "shelzys-fonts"
  4. Paste this entire file contents
  5. Save
  6. Then add this line to your theme.liquid <head> section (before </head>):
     {% render 'shelzys-fonts' %}
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- comment -%} Preconnect to Google Fonts for faster loading {%- endcomment -%}
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>

